\ Persistent-list behavior and shared-sequence regressions.

'check [ [ ] [ "list check failed" error ] ifelse ] def

( ) len 0 == check
( 1 2 3 ) len 3 == check
( 1 2 3 ) first 1 == check
( 1 2 3 ) last 3 == check
( 1 2 3 ) rest ( 2 3 ) == check
( ) rest ( ) == check
( 1 2 3 ) uncons ( 2 3 ) == check
1 == check
[ ( ) uncons ] [ "empty-list" ] try "empty-list" == check

( 2 3 ) dup 1 swap cons ( 1 2 3 ) == check
( 2 3 ) == check
( 1 2 ) 3 push-back ( 1 2 3 ) == check
( 1 2 3 ) reverse ( 3 2 1 ) == check
( 1 2 3 ) 2 take ( 1 2 ) == check
( 1 2 3 ) 2 dropn ( 3 ) == check

( 3 4 ) dup ( 1 2 ) swap concat ( 1 2 3 4 ) == check
( 3 4 ) == check

( 1 2 3 4 5 ) dup splitmid
( 3 4 5 ) == check
( 1 2 ) == check
( 1 2 3 4 5 ) == check

( 1 2 3 ) >list ( 1 2 3 ) == check
[ 1 2 3 ] >vector [ 1 2 3 ] == check
( 1 2 3 ) >vector [ 1 2 3 ] == check
[ 1 2 3 ] >list ( 1 2 3 ) == check

0 ( 1 2 3 4 ) [ + ] each 10 == check
0 ( 1 2 3 4 ) [ + ] fold 10 == check
( 1 2 3 ) [ 1 + ] map ( 2 3 4 ) == check
( 1 2 3 4 ) [ 2 % 0 == ] filter ( 2 4 ) == check
( 1 2 3 ) [ 3 == ] some true == check
( 1 2 3 ) [ 0 > ] all true == check

3 ( 1 2 3 4 ) [ > ] split
( 3 4 ) == check
( 1 2 ) == check
3 == check

( 1 3 5 ) ( 2 4 6 ) [ < ] merge ( 1 2 3 4 5 6 ) == check
( 1 2 3 ) 3 contains? true == check
( 1 2 3 ) 3 indexof 2 == check
( 1 2 1 3 ) unique ( 1 2 3 ) == check
( 3 1 2 ) sort ( 1 2 3 ) == check
( "a" "b" "c" ) "-" join "a-b-c" == check

( ( 'a 1 ) ( 'b 2 ) ) >map 'b get 2 == check
[ ( ( 'a 1 ) ( 'a 2 ) ) >map ] [ "duplicate-list-map" ] try
"duplicate-list-map" == check
( ( 2 "b" ) ( 1 "a" ) ) >pqueue pairs [ [ 1 "a" ] [ 2 "b" ] ] == check

[ ( 1 2 3 ) [ dup 2 == [ "bad" square ] [ 1 + ] ifelse ] map ]
[ "list-map-error" ] try "list-map-error" == check

\ Repeated cons builds in reverse order in O(n); one reverse restores order.
( ) [ 1 2 3 4 ] [ swap cons ] fold reverse ( 1 2 3 4 ) == check

\ Large enough to catch accidental indexed traversal of a list.
0 2000 range >list
dup 1999 contains? true == check
dup 1999 indexof 1999 == check
0 swap [ + ] fold 1999000 == check
